d one in the additional limit of the\nsmall cross-sectional area. For the unstable regime, we numerical solutions\ndemonstrate the spontaneous appearance of large oscillations in the\ncross-sectional area.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 May 2019 22:29:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 May 2019 18:49:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-14"}
